farmers%E2%80%99%20representatives%20in%20Chandigarh%20on%20Thursday%20(February%208)%20evening.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20meeting%20wound%20up%20at%20night%2C%20around%2010%20pm%2C%20Punjab%20chief%20minister%20Bhagwant%20Singh%20Mann%2C%20who%20was%20present%20during%20the%20meeting%2C%20told%20the%20media%20that%20Union%20government%20had%20taken%20a%20positive%20view%20on%20several%20of%20the%20demands%2C%20including%20withdrawing%20cases%20on%20farmers%20registered%20during%20the%20farm%20protest%20in%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20legalising%20the%20MSP%2C%20Mann%20said%20ministers%20did%20not%20commit%20but%20promised%20to%20take%20up%20the%20matter%20in%20detail%20with%20higher%20authorities%20in%20the%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMore%20rounds%20of%20meeting%20are%20possible%20in%20the%20near%20future%2C%20he%20said.%20The%20three%20ministers%20who%20represented%20the%20Union%20were%20junior%20agriculture%20minister%20Arjun%20Munda%2C%20junior%20home%20minister%20Nityanand%20Rai%20and%20commerce%20minister%20Piyush%20Goyal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20Jagjit%20Singh%20Dallewal%2C%20convener%20of%20the%20SKM%20(non-political)%2C%20who%20was%20a%20key%20negotiator%20from%20the%20farmers%E2%80%99%20side%20during%20the%20meeting%2C%20told%20the%20media%20that%20even%20though%20the%20meeting%20had%20a%20positive%20atmosphere%2C%20there%20was%20no%20plan%20to%20defer%20the%20programme%20of%20marching%20to%20Delhi%20on%20February%2013.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CCentral%20ministers%20have%20assured%20us%20that%20they%20will%20very%20soon%20hold%20another%20meeting.%20It%20will%20be%20in%20mutual%20interest%20if%20the%20Centre%20plans%20another%20meeting%20before%20February%2013%20and%20gives%20concrete%20solutions%20to%20our%20demands.%20Otherwise%20our%20call%20to%20march%20towards%20Delhi%20on%20February%2013%20stands%2C%E2%80%9D%20Dallewal%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDallewal%20said%20that%20several%20demands%20put%20before%20the%20Union%20ministers%20were%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20own%20previous%20assurances.%20For%20instance%2C%20when%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20was%20chief%20minister%20of%20Gujarat%2C%20he%20was%20a%20strong%20supporter%20of%20legalising%20the%20MSP.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20Centre%20even%20assured%20us%20of%20this%20step%20as%20part%20of%20the%20farm%20movement%20negotiation%20in%202020%20but%20it%20never%20took%20any%20concrete%20shape%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESecurity%20stepped%20up%20at%20borders%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20believe%20that%20the%20three%20Union%20ministers%20flying%20down%20to%20Chandigarh%20for%20the%20meeting%20was%20because%20of%20looming%20election%20season%20pressure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ruling%20BJP%2C%20hoping%20to%20win%20a%20third%20consecutive%20term%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20due%20in%20less%20than%20two%20months%2C%20does%20not%20want%20a%20replay%20of%20the%202020%20farm%20protest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20Centre%20has%20initiated%20talks%20with%20farm%20unions%2C%20they%20are%20also%20taking%20precautions.%20Security%20is%20being%20beefed%20up%20at%20all%20entries%20points%20towards%20Delhi%20from%20Punjab%2C%20Haryana%20and%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%2C%20it%20is%20learnt%2C%20is%20trying%20its%20level%20best%20to%20convince%20farmers%20to%20defer%20the%20%E2%80%98Delhi%20chalo%E2%80%99%20call.%20But%20if%20their%20programme%20continues%20as%20planned%2C%20the%20government%20is%20also%20taking%20steps%20to%20prevent%20farmers%20from%20reaching%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20said%20that%20the%20police%20are%20keeping%20a%20close%20eye%20on%20the%20movement%20of%20farmers%E2%80%99%20leaders%20heading%20the%20agitation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWho%20all%20are%20participating%20in%20the%20protest%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMore%20than%20200%20farmers%E2%80%99%20unions%20have%20planned%20to%20march%20to%20Delhi%20on%20February%2013%2C%20which%20will%20include%20around%20150%20unions%20of%20SKM%20(non-political)%20and%20around%2076%20unions%20under%20the%20banner%20of%20the%20KMSC.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESKM%20(non-political)%20is%20a%20breakaway%20faction%20of%20the%20SKM%2C%20which%20played%20a%20vital%20role%20in%20forcing%20the%20Modi%20government%20to%20take%20back%20three%20farm%20laws%20through%20a%20year-long%20protest%20outside%20Delhi%20in%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%202020%20protest%2C%20several%20unions%20in%20SKM%20went%20in%20different%20directions.%20Some%20fought%20elections%20and%20some%20committed%20to%20remain%20non-political.%20SKM%20(non-%20political)%20has%20been%20born%20of%20this%20churning%20and%20claims%20to%20have%20150%20farm%20unions%20as%20members%20from%20Punjab%2C%20Himachal%20Pradesh%2C%20Haryana%2C%20Rajasthan%2C%20UP%2C%20Uttarakhand%2C%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20West%20Bengal%20and%20other%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKMSC%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20is%20headed%20by%20Sarwan%20Singh%20Pandher%20and%20claims%20to%20have%20the%20support%20of%2050%20farm%20unions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20other%20SKM%20faction%20under%20Dr%20Darshan%20Pal%2C%20Yadvindra%20Yadav%20and%20others%20distanced%20itself%20from%20the%20%E2%80%98Dilli%20Chalo%E2%80%99%20protest%20call.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%20last%20week%2C%20SKM%20stated%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20national%20coordination%20committee%20of%20SKM%20held%20an%20online%20meeting%20and%20clarified%20that%20SKM%20has%20not%20given%20any%20call%20for%20%E2%80%98Dilli%20Chalo%E2%80%99.%20SKM%20has%20nothing%20to%20do%20with%20the%20decision%20of%20certain%20kisan%20organisations%20to%20protest%20in%20Delhi%20on%20February%2013.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707449904000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F09090639%2FGF0FvlvWQAExf0u.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fagriculture%2