3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%2035-minute%20interview%20to%20Karan%20Thapar%20for%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Karat%20reveals%20that%20her%20first%20big%20corporate%20battle%20happened%20when%20she%20was%20working%20for%20Air%20India%20in%20London%20in%201967.%20It%20had%20to%20do%20with%20the%20right%20to%20wear%20sarees%20rather%20than%20a%20mini%20skirt.%20She%20was%2020%20at%20the%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20in%20London%2C%20where%20she%20immersed%20herself%20in%20the%20%E2%80%9Cnational%20liberation%20struggle%20of%20Vietnam%E2%80%9D%20and%20was%20part%20of%20the%20famous%20Grosvenor%20Square%20protests%20of%201968%2C%20that%20she%20was%20first%20drawn%20to%20Marxism.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20her%20return%20to%20India%2C%20she%20joined%20the%20Communist%20Party%20Marxist%20and%20fell%20in%20love%20with%20Prakash%20Karat.%20When%20they%20decided%20to%20get%20married%2C%20they%20chose%20November%207%2C%20the%20anniversary%20of%20the%20Russian%20Revolution.%20But%2C%20actually%2C%20in%201917%2C%20the%20date%20in%20Russia%20was%2012%20days%20earlier%20(October%2025).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20reveals%3A%20%E2%80%9CI%20had%20no%20intention%20of%20being%20an%20ideal%20wife%20%E2%80%93%20communist%20or%20otherwise.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20challenges%20she%20faced%20was%20to%20navigate%20a%20career%20for%20herself%20around%20her%20husband%E2%80%99s%20position%20as%20a%20senior%20member%20of%20the%20same%20party%20and%2C%20eventually%2C%20the%20General%20Secretary%20of%20the%20CPM%20from%202005%20to%202015.%20%E2%80%9CI%20found%20that%20often%20my%20own%20identity%20as%20a%20communist%2C%20as%20a%20woman%2C%20as%20a%20whole-timer%20of%20the%20party%20for%20so%20many%20decades%2C%20was%20all%20conflated%20with%20my%20being%20Prakash%E2%80%99s%20wife.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20book%20is%20about%20the%20period%20from%201975%20to%201985%2C%20a%20decade%20during%20which%20she%20spent%20time%20in%20jail%20where%20she%20met%20Charles%20Sobhraj%2C%20who%20was%20accused%20of%20contempt%20of%20court%20and%20found%20guilty%20and%20punished.%20He%20was%20involved%20in%20several%20anti-dowry%20campaigns%20and%20worked%20diligently%20to%20help%20the%20Sikh%20community%20during%20the%20dreadful%20killings%20of%201984.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20Janata%20government%20years%2C%20when%20she%20was%20working%20with%20textile%20mill%20workers%2C%20Karat%20was%20falsely%20accused%20of%20trying%20to%20murder%20a%20police%20inspector%20whereas%20the%20truth%20was%20that%20he%20was%20guilty%20of%20beating%20her.%20She%20ended%20up%20spending%20time%20in%20jail.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FF2qISzy1mO8%3Fsi%3DxERBwE8eAEBNLY4j%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%20data-mce-type%3D%5C%22bookmark%5C%22%3E%EF%BB%BF%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707412230000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F08223752%2FKT-8-FEB-B-1.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fvideo%2Fwatch-educating-rita-the-early-years-of-brinda-karats-political-career%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20an%20interview%20to%20discuss%20her%20memoir%20'An%20Education%20for%20Rita'%2C%20Brinda%20Karat%20tells%20Karan%20Thapar%20that%20Rita%20was%20the%20name%20she%20was%20first%20given%20when%20she%20joined%20the%20CPI(M).%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fvideo%2Fwatch-educating-rita-the-early-years-of-brinda-karats-political-career%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Pakistan%20counts%20votes%20in%20election%20hit%20by%20violence%2C%20mobile%20outage%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707411969000%2C%22visual%22