aper%20on%20the%20Indian%20Economy%E2%80%99%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20the%2059-page%20document%20that%20was%20presented%20in%20the%20Lower%20House%20on%20Thursday%20says%20that%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20government%20inherited%20an%20economy%20that%20was%20%E2%80%9Cin%20a%20fragile%20state%3B%20public%20finances%20were%20in%20bad%20shape%3B%20there%20was%20economic%20mismanagement%20and%20financial%20indiscipline%3B%20and%20there%20was%20widespread%20corruption.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20%E2%80%9Ccrisis%20situation%E2%80%9D%20at%20the%20time%2C%20the%20paper%20said%20that%20the%20BJP%20government%20%E2%80%9Crefrained%20from%20bringing%20out%20a%20white%20paper%E2%80%9D%20because%20it%20would%20have%20given%20a%20%E2%80%9Cnegative%20narrative%20and%20shaken%20the%20confidence%20of%20all%2C%20including%20investors.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNow%20that%20we%20have%20stabilised%20the%20economy%20and%20set%20it%20on%20a%20recovery%20and%20growth%20path%2C%20it%20is%20necessary%20to%20place%20in%20the%20public%20domain%20the%20seemingly%20insurmountable%20challenges%20%E2%80%93%20left%20behind%20as%20a%20legacy%20by%20the%20UPA%20government%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20the%20White%20Paper%20was%20brought%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20objectives%2C%20the%20paper%20said%20that%20it%20seeks%20to%20inform%20MPs%20and%20the%20public%20about%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20nature%20and%20extent%20of%20governance%2C%20economic%20and%20fiscal%20crises%20that%20were%20bequeathed%20on%20this%20government%20when%20it%20assumed%20office%20in%202014%E2%80%9D%20and%20to%20inform%20the%20public%20about%20the%20measures%20taken%20by%20the%20BJP%20government%20to%20%E2%80%9Crestore%20the%20health%20of%20the%20economy%20and%20make%20it%20vigorous%20and%20capable%20of%20fulfilling%20the%20growth%20aspirations%20of%20the%20people%20in%20the%20present%20and%20in%20the%20Amrit%20Kaal.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20paper%20is%20divided%20into%20three%20parts%2C%20titled%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20inheritance%20of%20loss%E2%80%9D%2C%20%E2%80%9CPervasive%20corruption%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9CRescue%20of%20the%20economy%20from%20a%20state%20of%20crisis%2C%20despair%20and%20paralysis.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20part%20titled%20%E2%80%98The%20Inheritance%20of%20Loss%E2%80%99%20details%20how%20despite%20inheriting%20a%20healthy%20economy%20in%202004%2C%20the%20UPA%20government%20%E2%80%9Cmade%20it%20non-performing%E2%80%9D%20in%20ten%20years.%20This%2C%20the%20paper%20claims%2C%20was%20done%20through%20double-digit%20inflation%2C%20ailing%20banking%20sector%20following%20excessive%20lending%20during%20the%20boom%20phase%2C%20and%20high%20policy%20uncertainty%20that%20marred%20India%E2%80%99s%20business%20climate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%202014%2C%20our%20government%20inherited%20a%20deeply%20damaged%20economy%20whose%20foundations%20had%20to%20be%20rebuilt%20to%20enable%20self-sustaining%20long-term%20economic%20growth%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20second%20part%20%E2%80%98Pervasive%20Corruption%E2%80%99%2C%20it%20analyses%20the%20corruption%20scams%20under%20the%20UPA%20government%2C%20including%20in%20coal%20block%20allocation%2C%20Commonwealth%20Games%2C%202G%20telecom%2C%20Saradha%20chit%20fund%2C%20INX%20media%20case%2C%20Aircel-Maxis%2C%20Antrix-Devas%20Deal%2C%20land%20for%20jobs%2C%20Allotment%2FRelease%20of%20Prime%20Land%20in%20Panchkula%20and%20Gurgaon%2C%20J%26amp%3BK%20Cricket%20Association%2C%20Embraer%20Deal%2C%20Pilatus%20Basic%20Trainer%20Aircraft%2C%20Hawk%20Aircraft%20Purchase%2C%20Adarsh%20Housing%20Society%20Scam%2C%20and%20the%20Augusta%20Westland%20Helicopter%20Scam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20the%20coal%20block%2C%20Commonwealth%20Games%2C%202G%2C%20J%26amp%3BK%20cricket%20association%2C%20the%20paper%20lists%20the%20remaining%20scams%20without%20providing%20details%20of%20the%20amount%20of%20corruption%20involved.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20third%20part%2C%20titled%20%E2%80%98Rescue%20of%20the%20economy%20from%20a%20state%20of%20crisis%2C%20despair%20and%20paralysis%E2%80%99%2C%20the%20paper%20says%20that%20due%20to%20measures%20taken%20by%20the%20BJP%20government%2C%20India%20transitioned%20from%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20league%20of%20%E2%80%98Fragile%20Five%E2%80%99%20to%20the%20league%20of%20%E2%80%98Top%20Five%E2%80%99%20in%20just%20about%20a%20decade.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20saying%20that%20it%20has%20gone%20from%20being%20the%2010th%20largest%20in%202014%2C%20it%20has%20become%20the%20fifth%20largest%20in%202023%20and%20adds%20that%20%E2%80%9C..(but%20for%20the%20pandemic%20in%202020%2C%20we%20would%20have%20become%20the%20fifth%20largest%20at%20least%20two%20years%20earlier)%20and%20is%20slated%20to%20become%20the%20third%20largest%20by%202027%2C%20as%20per%20IMF%20projections.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98Amrit%20Kal%20has%20begun%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20conclusion%2C%20the%20paper%20does%20a%20comparative%20analysis%20of%20the%20UPA%20and%20the%20National%20Democratic%20Alliance%20(NDA)%20governments%20and%20says%20that%20in%20comparison%20to%20the%202G%20and%204G%20scams%20under%20the%20UPA%2C%20India%20now%20has%20the%20lowest%20%5Bdata%5D%20rates%20and%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20fastest%20rollout%20of%205G%20in%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20says%20that%20in%20comparison%20to%20the%20Coalgate%20scam%2C%20the%20Modi%20government%20built%20%E2%80%9Csystems%20for%20transparent%20and%20objective%20auctions%20for%20harnessing%20natural%20resources%20to%20boost%20the%20economy%20and%20the%20public%20finances%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Cset%20up%20a%20bullion%20exchange%20in%20GIFT%20IFSC%20with%20a%20transparent%20mechanism%20for%20import.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20regard%20to%20inflation%2C%20it%20states%20that%20in%20comparison%20to%20the%20double-digit%20inflation%20under%20the%20UPA%20government%2C%20inflation%20has%20now%20been%20brought%20down%20to%20over%205%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThen%2C%20we%20had%20a%20foreign%20exchange%20crisis%3B%20now%2C%20we%20have%20record%20foreign%20exchange%20reserves%20of%20over%20%24620%20billion%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20paper%20concludes%20that%20looking%20back%20at%20the%20past%20decade%2C%20the%20Modi%20government%20has%20successfully%20overcome%20the%20challenges%20left%20behind%20by%20the%20previous%20government.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Amrit%20Kaal%20has%20just%20begun%20and%20our%20destination%20is%20%E2%80%98India%20a%20developed%20nation%20by%202047.%E2%80%99%20It%20is%20our%20Kartavya%20Kaal%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20despite%20being%20a%20lower-middle-income%20economy%2C%20India%20will%20have%20not%20one%20but%20two%20centi-billionaires%20%E2%80%93%20Mukesh%20Ambani%20and%20Gautam%20Adani%20%E2%80%93%20in%202024.%20And%2C%20t%3Cspan%3Ehis%20in%20a%20country%20where%20800%20million%20people%20still%20depend%20on%20free%20food%20from%20the%20government%20to%20get%20by%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.economictimes.com%2Fnews%2Findia%2Fambani-adani-tata-jindal-the-four-pillars-of-indian-team-boosting-modis-self-reliance-vision%2Famp_articleshow%2F106463092.cms%5C%22%3Ewrites%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Cem%3EBloomberg%3C%2Fem%3E%20columnist%20Andy%20Mukherjee.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707408713000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F03%2F24160818%2FScreenshot-2023-03-24-at-4.07.15-PM_cleanup.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fcentre-tables-white-paper-on-10-years-of-upa-hours-after-congresss-black-paper-on-modi-govts-failures%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Titled%20'White%20Paper%20on%20the%20Indian%20Economy'%2C%20the%2059-page%20document%20says%20that%20the%20BJP%20government%20inherited%20an%20economy%20that%20was%20%E2%80%9Cin%20a