2.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3ELed%20by%20chief%20minister%20Siddaramaiah%2C%20Karnataka%20Congress%20ministers%2C%20MLAs%2C%20and%20MPs%20converged%20at%20Jantar%20Mantar%20in%20Delhi%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20February%207%2C%20over%20the%20non-payment%20of%20dues%20by%20the%20Narendra%20Modi-led%20Union%20government%20and%20the%20%E2%80%9Cgross%20injustice%E2%80%9D%20being%20meted%20out%20by%20tax%20devolution%20formula%20by%20the%2015th%20Finance%20Commission.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9CWe%2C%20Kannadigas%2C%20pay%20taxes%20of%20Rs%20430%2C000%20crore.%20But%20we%20receive%20only%20Rs%2050%2C000%20crore%20back.%20That%20means%20out%20of%20every%20Rs%20100%2C%20only%20Rs%2013%20comes%20back%20to%20us.%20Can%20there%20be%20greater%20injustice%20than%20this%3F%20Should%20we%20tolerate%20this%20injustice%3F%E2%80%9D%20said%20Siddaramaiah%20at%20the%20protest.%20%E2%80%9CInjustice%20with%20regard%20to%20tax%20to%20the%20tune%20of%20Rs%2062%2C098%20crore%20has%20been%20done%20to%20the%20state%20by%20the%2015th%20Finance%20Commission.%20Shouldn%E2%80%99t%20we%20question%20this%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%2015th%20Finance%20Commission%20is%20a%20constitutional%20body%2C%20and%20its%20primary%20function%20is%20to%20recommend%20the%20distribution%20of%20tax%20proceeds%20between%20the%20Union%20government%20and%20the%20states%2C%20as%20well%20as%20among%20the%20states%20themselves.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Union%20finance%20minister%2C%20Nirmala%20Sitharaman%2C%20denied%20the%20accusations%20levelled%20by%20the%20Karnataka%20government.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20Congress-led%20Karnataka%20government%20has%20a%20%E2%80%98separatist%E2%80%99%20mindset%20and%20is%20spreading%20a%20%E2%80%98false%20narrative%E2%80%99%20about%20the%20Centre%E2%80%99s%20alleged%20discrimination%20against%20the%20state%20in%20fund%20allocation.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3ECongress%