%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20financial%20year%202022-2-23%2C%20public%20funds%20worth%20Rs%2034%2C01%2C05%2C848%20was%20spent%20to%20charter%20flights%20and%20helicopters%20for%20the%20chief%20minister%20and%20other%20dignitaries.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFrom%20January%202023%20to%20January%202024%2C%20the%20amount%20spent%20was%20Rs%2014%2C02%2C19%2C313.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThough%20the%20sum%20cited%20by%20the%20Sarma%20government%20for%20the%202022-2023%20financial%20year%20matched%20with%20an%20earlier%20statement%20placed%20at%20the%20assembly%20last%20September%2C%20it%2C%20however%2C%20hugely%20overshot%20the%20amount%20cited%20by%20it%20in%20an%20RTI%20reply%20given%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3ECrossCurrent%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%20September.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAfter%20the%20state%20government%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20the%20RTI%20application%20filed%20on%20August%2022%2C%202022%20for%20nearly%20a%20year%2C%20the%20Guwahati-based%20news%20portal%20had%20appealed%20to%20the%20State%20Information%20Commission%2C%20seeking%20a%20reply.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cins%3EThe%20detailed%20reports%20can%20be%20read%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fassam-himanta-biswa-sarma-public-money-helicopter-chartered-flights-bjp-party-wedding%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fassam-cmo-says-expenses-for-party-work-are-paid-for-by-the-political-party-but-rti-details-dont-bear-that-out%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20commission%2C%20on%20August%208%2C%202023%2C%20directed%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20General%20Administration%20Department%20to%20provide%20the%20information%20asked%20for%20through%20RTI.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20September%202023%2C%20the%20state%20government%20shared%20information%20but%20only%20partially.%20The%20RTI%20application%20had%20also%20sought%20details%20on%20such%20spending%20from%20May%2010%2C%202021%20till%20date.%20May%2010%2C%202021%20was%20the%20day%20the%20new%20chief%20minister%2C%20Sarma%2C%20was%20sworn%20in%20after%20the%20BJP%20won%20the%20state%20assembly%20elections%20for%20the%20second%20time%2C%20replacing%20the%20incumbent%20chief%20minister%20Sarbananda%20Sonowal.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20CrossCurrent%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%99s%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fassam-himanta-biswa-sarma-public-money-helicopter-chartered-flights-bjp-party-wedding%5C%22%3Ejoint%20report%20based%20on%20the%20partial%20RTI%20reply%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20the%20Sarma%20government%20showed%20that%20the%20state%20government%20had%20spent%20crores%20in%20the%20chief%20minister%E2%80%99s%20non-governmental%20activities%20%E2%80%93%20which%20included%20attending%20high%20profile%20weddings%20within%20and%20outside%20Assam%20and%20engaging%20in%20his%20party%E2%80%99s%20work%20including%20campaigning%20for%20party%20leaders%20and%20its%20allies%20by%20violating%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20model%20code%20of%20conduct.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThough%20the%20chief%20minister%E2%80%99s%20office%20responded%20to%20the%20RTI%20based%20report%20by%20calling%20it%20a%20%E2%80%9Chit%20job%E2%80%9D%20and%20claimed%20that%20the%20BJP%20had%20paid%20for%20Sarma%E2%80%99s%20non-governmental%20work%2C%20it%20could%20not%20produce%20any%20proof%20of%20it%20immediately.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20RTI%20reply%20of%20the%20Sarma%20government%2C%20furthermore%2C%20bore%20the%20facts%20which%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fassam-cmo-says-expenses-for-party-work-are-paid-for-by-the-political-party-but-rti-details-dont-bear-that-out%5C%22%3Epublished%20in%20response%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20the%20CMO%E2%80%99s%20statement%20put%20out%20on%20X.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707383615000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F08144104%2FGFlamxXa0AAQFxW.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fhimanta-chartered-flights-helicopter-assam-assembly%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20government's%20response%20in%20the%20Assam%20assembly%20comes%20three%20days%20after%20The%20Wire%20and%20The%20Crosscurrent%20published%20a%20joint%20report%20on%20the%20state%20government%20spending%20crores%20on%20CM%20Himanta%20Biswa%20Sarma%E2%80%99s%20travel%20on%20non-government%20business%20by%20chartered%20flights.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A69%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fhimanta-chartered-flights-helicopter-assam-assembly%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Messi's%20Inter%20Miami%20accused%20of%20'deliberate%20and%20calculated%20snub'%20against%20Hong%20Kong%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707383580000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F24%2F02%2F768x432%2Fskynews-lionel-messi-inter-miami_6448351.jpg%3F20240208102258%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Flionel-messis-inter-miami-accused-of-deliberate-and-calculated-snub-against-hong-kong-13066617%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Lionel%20Messi%20and%20Inter%20Miami%20have%20been%20accused%20of%20a%20%26quot%3Bdeliberate%20and%20calculated%20snub%26quot%3B%20against%20Hong%20Kong.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A114%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Flionel-messis-inter-miami-accused-of-deliberate-and-calculated-snub-against-hong-kong-13066617%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Flionel-messis-inter-miami-accused-of-deliberate-and-calculated-snub-against-hong-kong-13066617%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Flionel-messis-inter-miami-accused-of-deliberate-and-calculated-snub-against-hong-kong-13066617%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Uneggceptable%3A%20Maharashtra%20Gov%20Says%20No%20Eggs%20in%20Midday%20Meal%20if%2040%25%20Students%20Vote%20Against%20It%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F12162717%2F10191445986_676a099cd6_c.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20controversy%20around%20including%20eggs%20in%20mid-day%20meals%20has%20resurfaced%20once%20again%2C%20with%20the%20Maharashtra%20government%20amending%20a%20government%20resolution%20(GR)%20that%20mandated%20students%20in%20the%20state%20be%20served%20eggs%20once%20a%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20move%20comes%20in%20wake%20of%20opposition%20from%20religious%20outfits%20like%20the%20Shree%20Mumbai%20Jain%20Sangh%20Sangathan%20(SMJSS)%2C%20an%20organisation%20representing%20the%20city%E2%80%99s%20Jain%20community%2C%20and%20members%20of%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20spiritual%20cell%2C%20%3Cem%3EMidday%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mid-day.com%2Fmumbai%2Fmumbai-news%2Farticle%2Fmumbai-just-40-per-cent-veggie-militants-enough-to-deny-eggs-for-schoolchildren-23334063%3Fcity-news-breakingnews%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20earlier%20version%20of%20the%20GR%20allowed%20parents%20to%20choose%20if%20they%20wanted%20their%20child%20to%20be%20served%20eggs%20or%20opt%20for%20bananas%20as%20a%20substitute.%20However%2C%20the%20amended%20GR%20has%20revoked%20the%20option%20to%20choose%20between%20vegetarian%20and%20non-vegetarian%20meal%20options.%20Now%2C%20eggs%20will%20not%20be%20served%20to%20anyone%20in%20a%20school%20if%2040%25%20of%20the%20students%20there%20do%20not%20consent%20to%20consuming%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20GR%20also%20specifies%20that%20schools%20receiving%20meals%20from%20Akshaya%20Patra%20and%20Annamrita%20Foundation%2C%20charities%20affiliated%20with%20the%20International%20Society%20for%20Krishna%20Consciousness%20(ISKCON)%2C%20will%20be%20exempted%20from%20serving%20eggs%2C%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20mid-day%20meal%20scheme%20provides%20nutritious%20food%20to%20around%20two%20crore%20students%20studying%20in%20government-run%20schools.%20In%20a%20bid%20to%20improve%20the%20students%E2%80%99%20diet%2C%20it%20was%20decided%20that%20instead%20of%20just%20khichdi%2C%20they%20would%20be%20served%20egg%20pulao%2C%20biryani%2C%20sweets%2C%20vegetables%20and%20fruits.%20This%20was%20the%20first%20time%20in%2020%20years%20that%20the%20school%20education%20department%20had%20decided%20to%20reintroduce%20eggs%20to%20the%20mid-day%20meal%20menu%2C%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20after%20a%20presentation%20was%20given%20to%20chief%20minister%20Eknath%20Shinde%20and%20school%20education%20minister%20Deepak%20Kesarkar%20by%20the%20trustees%20and%20members%20of%20SMJSS%20on%20January%205%2C%20the%20government%20issued%20a%20fresh%20GR%20on%20January%2024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fkarnataka-midday-meal-brahminical-sattvic-egg%5C%22%3EWho%20Gains%20When%20Karnataka%E2%80%99s%20Children%20Don%E2%80%99t%20Get%20Eggs%20in%20Their%20Midday%20Meals%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVirag%20Shah%20from%20SMJSS%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mid-day.com%2Fmumbai%2Fmumbai-news%2Farticle%2Fmumbai-just-40-per-cent-veggie-militants-enough-to-deny-eggs-for-schoolchildren-23334063%3Fcity-news-breakingnews%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CDuring%20the%20presentation%2C%20we%20highlighted%20that%20under%20the%20new%20mid-day%20meal%20plan%2C%20approximately%20four%20crore%20chicks%20per%20month%20and%20at%20least%2036%20crore%20chicks%20per%20year%20(excluding%20the%20vacation%20period)%20would%20be%20sacrificed%20for%20egg%20production.%20Now%2C%20as%20a%20result%20of%20the%20changes%20in%20the%20notification%2C%20nearly%202.25%20crore%20and%2020%20crore%20chicks%20per%20month%20and%20year%20respectively%20will%20be%20spared.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20religious%20group%20further%20alleged%20that%20inclusion%20of%20eggs%20in%20the%20mid-day%20meal%20scheme%20was%20designed%20to%20benefit%20the%20poultry%20industry.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20no%20demand%20for%20eggs%20from%20any%20of%20the%20stakeholders.%20The%20state%E2%80%99s%20intention%20to%20support%20the%20poultry%20farmers%20will%20prove%20futile.%20The%20scheme%20will%20impose%20a%20huge%20economic%20burden%20on%20the%20state%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mid-day.com%2Fmumbai%2Fmumbai-news%2Farticle%2Fmumbai-just-40-per-cent-veggie-militants-enough-to-deny-eggs-for-schoolchildren-23334063%3Fcity-news-breakingnews%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20without%20explaining%20why%20or%20how%20it%20would%20prove%20to%20be%20an%20economic%20burden.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20PM%20POSHAN%20scheme%20does%20not%20recommend%20eggs%20in%20its%20entire%20scheme.%20It%20advocates%20culturally%20accepted%20food.%20In%20Maharashtra%2C%20where%20the%20vegetarian%20population%20is%2040%25%2C%20eggs%20cannot%20be%20called%20culturally%20accepted%20food%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20outfit%20claimed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20principal%20of%20a%20BMC%20school%20in%20south%20Mumbai%20said%20that%20the%20GR%20made%20it%20very%20clear%20that%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mid-day.com%2Fmumbai%2Fmumbai-news%2Farticle%2Fmumbai-just-40-per-cent-veggie-militants-enough-to-deny-eggs-for-schoolchildren-23334063%3Fcity-news-breakingnews%5C%22%3E%20no%20one%20was%20going%20to%20be%20forced%20to%20eat%20eggs.%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20decided%20that%20students%20at%20government-run%20and%20aided%20students%20would%20get%20an%20egg%20a%20week%2C%20either%20boiled%20or%20as%20part%20of%20other%20preparations%20such%20as%20pulao%20or%20biryani%2C%20while%20vegetarian%20students%20and%20those%20who%20don%E2%80%99t%20want%20the%20eggs%20would%20be%20served%20fruits.%20It%20was%20clear%20and%20nobody%20was%20going%20to%20be%20forced%20to%20eat%20eggs.%20These%20objections%20and%20the%20amendments%20made%20to%20the%20GR%20are%20illogical.%20My%20domestic%20help%E2%80%99s%20daughter%20studies%20at%20a%20BMC%20school.%20They%20prefer%20eggs.%20Just%20because%2040%25%20of%20students%2Fparents%20vote%20against%20eggs%2C%20she%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20get%20eggs%20with%20her%20meal.%20How%20is%20that%20fair%3F%E2%80%9D%20the%20principal%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECriticising%20the%20restriction%2C%20Prasad%20Gokhale%2C%20a%20parent%20and%20convenor%20of%20Marathi%20Shala%20Aaapan%20Tikavlya%20Pajihet%2C%20a%20parents%E2%80%99%20awareness%20group%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mid-day.com%2Fmumbai%2Fmumbai-news%2Farticle%2Fmumbai-just-40-per-cent-veggie-militants-enough-to-deny-eggs-for-schoolchildren-23334063%3Fcity-news-breakingnews%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20vegetarians%2C%20and%20would%20not%20prefer%20eggs%20in%20the%20meal.%20However%2C%20just%20because%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%2C%20we%20cannot%20make%20others%20follow%20our%20preferences.%20Many%20dieticians%20and%20nutritionists%20recommend%20eggs%2C%20citing%20health%20benefits.%20Instead%20of%20relying%20on%20religious%20groups%2C%20the%20state%20government%20should%20have%20relied%20on%20experts%20to%20make%20these%20changes.%20This%20new%20kind%20of%20discrimination%20has%20now%20become%20a%20trend.%20I%20disagree%20with%20these%20amendments.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDoctors%20and%20nutritionists%20have%20time%20and%20again%20pointed%20out%20that%20eggs%20are%20an%20important%20source%20of%20protein%20in%20the%20Indian%20diet%20that%20is%20otherwise%20high%20in%20carbohydrates.%E2%80%9CEggs%20offer%20significant%20nutritional%20value%20as%20they%20provide%20high-quality%20protein.%20While%20it%E2%80%99s%20possible%20to%20replace%20them%20with%20plant-based%20proteins%2C%20such%20alternatives%20may%20be%20costly%20and%20impractical.%20A%20single%20egg%20can%20easily%20fulfil%20a%20child%E2%80%99s%20daily%20protein%20requirements%2C%E2%80%9D%20Dr%20Hema%20Yadav%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERights%20activists%2C%20including%20those%20involved%20in%20the%20Right%20to%20Food%20Campaign%2C%20have%20also%20pointed%20out%20why%20serving%20eggs%20to%20children%20is%20important%20under%20the%20midday%20meal%20scheme.%20%E2%80%9COne%20must%20recognize%20that%20the%20problem%20is%20not%20just%20the%20absence%20of%20eggs%20from%20the%20menu%20at%20schools%20and%20anganwadis.%20The%20menu%20lacks%20diversity%20in%20the%20form%20of%20milk%2C%20dairy%2C%20vegetables%2C%20fats%2Foils%2C%20pulses%20and%20legumes%20in%20many%20of%20the%20States.%20The%20prevalence%20of%20nutritional%20deficiency%2C%20stunting%2C%20underweight%20and%20other%20kinds%20of%20health%20issues%20is%20higher%20in%20the%20children%20belonging%20to%20marginalized%20communities.%20Due%20to%20the%20vicious%20combination%20of%20malnutrition%20and%20illness%2C%20the%20children%20and%20families%20of%20these%20communities%20are%20the%20most%20vulnerable%20without%20the%20intervention%20of%20the%20state.%20Eggs%20in%20these%20scenarios%20can%20tilt%20the%20nutritional%20status%20of%20a%20child%20and%20would%20help%20gaining%20essential%20nutrients%20in%20fighting%20malnutrition%20and%20ill%20health%20conditions.%20Eggs%20provide%20many%20of%20the%20nutritional%20needs%20including%20good%20quality%20proteins%2C%20minerals%2C%20vitamins%20and%20fats.%20They%20are%20easy%20to%20cook%2C%20not%20prone%20to%20adulteration%20and%20pilferage%20like%20other%20foods%20and%20contribute%20to%20increasing%20school%20attendance%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20Campaign%20had%20said%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcountercurrents.org%2F2021%2F12%2Fegg-in-mid-day-meals-resistance-is-against-child-rights%2F%5C%22%3E2021%20press%20release%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707382234000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F12162717%2F10191445986_676a099cd6_c.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feducation%2Funeggceptable-maharashtra-gov-says-no-eggs-in-midday-meal-if-40-students-vote-against-it%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Earlier%20parents%20could%20choose%20if%20they%20wanted%20their%20child%20to%20be%20served%20eggs%20or%20opt%20for%20bananas%20as%20a%20substitute.%20Now%2C%20eggs%20will%20not%20be%20served%20to%20anyone%20in%20a%20school%20if%2040%25%20of%20the%20students%20there%20do%20not%20consent%20to%20consuming%20them.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A22%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feducation%2Funeggceptable-maharashtra-gov-says-no-eggs-in-midday-meal-if-40-students-vote-against-it%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Farmers%20on%20Their%20Way%20to%20Protest%20at%20Parliament%20Stopped%20at%20Delhi-UP%20Border%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F08141152%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-02-08-at-1.00.13-PM.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Reports%20from%20the%20Delhi-Uttar%20Pradesh%20border%20are%20coming%20in%20of%20the%20administration%20in%20UP%20stopping%20NCR%20farmers%20from%20entering%20Delhi.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Fvijaita%2Fstatus%2F1755501645096706220%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9CWater%20cannons%2C%20bulldozers%2C%20cranes%2C%20several%20RAF%20and%20police%20personnel%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20there%2C%20stop%20them%20from%20entering%20the%20national%20capital.%20There%20are%20also%20buses%20on%20standby%20to%20probably%20%E2%80%9Cdetain%20people%20who%20violate%20prohibitory%20orders%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EF