22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newsclick.in%2Fnoida-farmers-open-front-against-ntpc-dadri-agitation-continues%23%3A~%3Atext%3DThese%2520farmers%2520of%252024%2520villages%2Calso%2520launched%2520a%2520long%2520movement.%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ENewsclick%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20On%20December%2018%2C%202023%2C%20farmers%20sat%20on%20strike%20in%20front%20of%20the%20NTPC%20office%20located%20in%20Noida%20Sector-24.%20After%20the%20police%20stopped%20the%20protesters%20some%20distance%20before%20the%20main%20gate%20of%20NTPC%2C%20they%20staged%20a%20day%20and%20night%20strike%20there.%20These%20farmers%20of%2024%20villages%20say%20that%20they%20are%20affected%20by%20NTPC%E2%80%99s%20Dadri%20plant.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20protest%20is%20being%20led%20by%20Bharatiya%20Kisan%20Parishad%20leader%20Sukhbir%20Khalifa.%20He%20said%20that%20%E2%80%9CFarmers%20protested%20at%20NTPC%20Dadri%20for%20several%20months%20and%20also%20launched%20a%20long%20movement.%20During%20this%2C%20several%20rounds%20of%20talks%20were%20held%20with%20the%20administration%20in%20which%20the%20demands%20of%20the%20farmers%20were%20considered%20justified%20but%20till%20now%20those%20demands%20have%20not%20been%20met.%20That%E2%80%99s%20why%20we%20have%20come%20this%20time%20to%20fight%20a%20decisive%20battle.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENewsclick%3C%2Fem%3E%20also%20reported%20on%20NTPC%E2%80%99s%20press%20release%20issued%20in%20December%20saying%2C%20%E2%80%9Cto%20meet%20the%20need%20of%20electricity%20in%20the%20national%20interest%20including%20NCR%2C%20the%20construction%20of%20Stage-1%20of%20National%20Capital%20Power%20Station%20(NCPS)%20in%20Dadri%20region%20has%20been%20going%20on%20since%201986.%201995.%20The%20land%20acquisition%20and%20compensation%20were%20done%20as%20per%20the%20Land%20Acquisition%20Act%20existing%20at%20that%20time%20and%20the%20instructions%20of%20the%20district%20administration.%E2%80%9D%20NTPC%20also%20said%20that%20%E2%80%9Cafter%20so%20many%20years%2C%20the%20protest%20is%20being%20held%20again%20with%20some%20demands.%20From%20time%20to%20time%2C%20during%20various%20talks%20with%20the%20protesters%2C%20NSPC%20has%20made%20it%20known%20that%20equal%20compensation%20and%20employment%20is%20now%20no%20longer%20possible%20to%20consider.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707381786000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F08141152%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-02-08-at-1.00.13-PM.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fagriculture%2Ffarmers-on-their-way-to-protest-at-parliament-stopped-at-delhi-up-border%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Reports%20are%20coming%20in%20of%20farmers%20having%20blocked%20the%20Noida-Greater%20Noida%20Expressway.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A18%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fagriculture%2Ffarmers-on-their-way-to-protest-at-parliament-stopped-at-delhi-up-border%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Bharat%20Ratna%20to%20LK%20Advani%20Signals%20the%20Grand%20Success%20of%20Communal%20Politics%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F08123957%2FEffect-2024-02-08T123938.496.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20veteran%20politician%20of%20the%20BJP%2C%20Lal%20Krishna%20Advani%2C%20has%20been%20awarded%20the%20Bharat%20Ratna%2C%20the%20highest%20civilian%20award%20in%20the%20country.%20He%20joins%20the%20list%20of%20right-wing%20leaders%20and%20intellectuals%20like%20Madan%20Mohan%20Malviya%2C%20Nananji%20Deshmukh%2C%20and%20Atal%20Bihari%20Vajpayee%2C%20who%20have%20been%20conferred%20this%20title%20by%20the%20Modi%20government.%20The%20conferring%20of%20Bharat%20Ratna%20coincides%20with%20the%20consecration%20of%20Ram%20Temple%20in%20Ayodhya%20on%20the%20disputed%20site%20where%20the%20Babri%20Masjid%20stood.%20It%20was%20demolished%20by%20the%20Karsewaks%2C%20the%20pack%20of%20militant%20Hindu%20nationalists%20mobilised%20by%20the%20BJP-RSS%20and%20its%20allied%20organisation%20to%20reconstruct%20the%20Ram%20Temple.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20moment%20warrants%20our%20attention%20to%20what%20exceptional%20service%20of%20the%20highest%20order%20qualifies%20Advani%20for%20Bharat%20Ratna%2C%20revisiting%20his%20political%20legacy%20and%20contribution%20to%20Indian%20politics.%20This%20brings%20us%20to%20the%20time%20of%20aggressive%20Hindutva%20posturing%20through%20the%20Rath%20Yatra%20in%20the%2090s%2C%20whose%20architect-in-chief%20was%20Advani.%20Now%20retired%20from%20active%20political%20life%2C%20Advani%20is%20the%20early%20incarnation%20of%20aggressive%20right-wing%20Hindutva%20politics%20in%20the%20country%2C%20which%20fundamentally%20altered%20the%20language%20of%20Indian%20politics.%20He%20is%20the%20founding%20member%20of%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20unapologetic%20leader%20of%20militant%20Hindutva%20politics%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Ram%20Janmabhoomi%20Andolan%20came%20as%20a%20watershed%20moment%20in%20Indian%20politics%20and%20made%20the%20ideology%20of%20Hindutva%20the%20political%20mainstream.%20The%20Ram%20Janmabhoomi%20Yatra%20served%20multiple%20purposes%2C%20the%20most%20sacred%20being%20the%20political%20revival%20of%20right-wing%20Hindutva%20politics.%20It%20was%20during%20this%20time%20that%20Hindutva%20politics%20took%20a%20major%20militant%20turn.%20Lumpen%20organisations%20like%20Bajrang%20Dal%20and%20Vishwa%20Hindu%20Parishad%20became%20compulsory%20elements%20in%20composing%20communal%20violence%20and%20polarising%20the%20electorate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Hindu%20right%E2%80%99s%20search%20for%20a%20new%20lease%20of%20political%20life%20brought%20the%20Ram%20Janmabhoomi%20movement%20to%20the%20epicentre%20of%20political%20mobilisation.%20Ram%20mandir%20andolan%20was%20also%20an%20upper-caste%20conservative%20revolution%20that%20brought%20the%20Hindu%20majority%E2%80%99s%20religious%20sentiments%20to%20the%20centre%20of%20political%20discourse%20to%20limit%20the%20impact%20of%20Mandal%20democratisation%20and%20create%20a%20political%20Hindu%20vote%20bank%20through%20the%20cooptation%20of%20non-dominant%20castes%20and%20organised%20enmity%20against%20minorities.%20The%20organised%20enmity%20against%20Muslims%20became%20the%20mass%20mobilisation%20plank%20of%20Hindutva%20politics%20since%20the%20time%20of%20Advani%2C%20whose%20most%20evocative%20display%20happened%20during%20the%20Ram%20Janmabhoomi%20Yatra.%20Advani%20occasionally%20expressed%20his%20inherent%20disdain%20against%20the%20subaltern%20political%20assertion%20by%20accusing%20Mandal%20politics%20of%20dividing%20Hindus%2C%20which%20the%20Yatra%20undone%20through%20a%20spiritual%20unity%20amongst%20Hindus.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fl-k-advani-from-rath-yatra-to-bharat-ratna%5C%22%3ELK%20Advani%3A%20From%20Rath%20Yatra%20to%20Bharat%20Ratna%2C%20a%20Political%20Journey%20Propelled%20By%20Violence%2C%20Polarisation%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20political%20spirituality%20of%20Rath%20Yatra%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20procession%20of%20Rath%20Yatra%20was%20designed%20to%20create%20a%20political%20awakening%20of%20the%20Hindu%20nation%2C%20standing%20united%20with%20anger%20against%20the%20civilisational%20assault%20over%20religion%2C%20which%20continued%20even%20after%20independence%20through%20pseudo-secularism.%20As%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fbooks.google.co.in%2Fbooks%2Fabout%2FRoutine_Violence.html%3Fid%3Dca7qES8Z9hAC%26redir_esc%3Dy%5C%22%3EGyanendra%20Pandey%3C%2Fa%3E%20explains%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20conflict%20over%20the%20Babri%20Masjid%20in%20Ayodhya%20is%20part%20of%20a%20larger%20Hindu%20drive%20to%20reclaim%20the%20national%20culture%20from%20its%20enemies%20%E2%80%93Muslims%2C%20but%20also%20secularists%20and%20Westernisers.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20chariot-themed%20design%20of%20Toyota%20Van%20had%20the%20portrait%20of%20Advani%20with%20slogans%20making%20clarion%20calls%20in%20support%20of%20the%20Ram%20Mandir%20movement.%20Writing%20about%20Babri%20Masjid%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fbooks.google.co.in%2Fbooks%2Fabout%2FMaking_India_Hindu.html%3Fid%3DnnJ1AAAAMAAJ%26redir_esc%3Dy%5C%22%3ERichard%20Davis%3C%2Fa%3E%20mentions%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20choice%20of%20site%20juxtaposes%20two%20figures%20well%20known%20to%20most%20people%20in%20north%20India%3A%20Ram%20and%20Babar.%20As%20God%20and%20human%2C%20they%20are%20made%20to%20stand%20for%20two%20religions%20%E2%80%93%20Hinduism%20and%20Islam%20%E2%80%93%20in%20a%20highly%20imbalanced%20manner%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20movement%20had%20a%20mass%20orientation%2C%20intended%20to%20create%20a%20communal%20commotion%20and%20carve%20a%20sacred%20nation%20space%2C%20with%20Ayodhya%20at%20its%20centre.%20%C2%A0This%20projected%C2%A0%20Ram%20Janmabhoomi%20as%20a%20national%20issue%20whose%20liberation%20entailed%20undoing%20the%20historical%20wrongs%20inflicted%20by%20the%20Muslim%20others%20on%20the%20Hindu%20religion.%20The%2035-day%20Yatra%20of%20Advani%20had%20an%20approximate%2010%2C000%20km%20long%20route%2C%20covering%20eight%20North%20Indian%20states%20of%20Sangh%20stronghold%20in%20the%20Hindi%20heartland.%20It%20started%20from%20Somnath%20temple%2C%20having%20symbolic%20importance%20to%20the%20Hindutva%20assertion.%20For%20Advani%2C%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20reconstruction%20of%20Somnath%20was%20the%20first%20chapter%20in%20a%20journey%20to%20pre%C2%ADserve%20the%20old%20symbols%20of%20unity%2C%20communal%20amity%2C%20and%20cultural%20oneness%20to%20be%20succeeded%20by%20the%20Ram%20Janmabhoomi%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20984px)%2061vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2045vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F12%2F15133951%2Fmodi-advani.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Narendra%20Modi%20with%20L.K.%20Advani%20during%20Advani's%20rath%20yatra.%20Credit%3A%20Twitter%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22646%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F12%2F15133951%2Fmodi-advani.jpg%20454w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F12%2F15133951%2Fmodi-advani-300x272.jpg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-205233%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22585%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ENarendra%20Modi%20with%20L.K.%20Advani%20during%20Advani%E2%80%99s%20rath%20yatra.%20Credit%3A%20Twitter%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20event%20witnessed%20the%20active%20participation%20of%20Sangh%E2%80%99s%20militant%20subsidiary%20organisations%20armed%20with%20weapons%2C%20bringing%20a%20militant%20Hindutva%20zeal%20to%20the%20yatra.%20The%20violent%20ceremonious%20processions%20were%20actively%20endorsed%20and%20supported%20by%20Advani.%20He%20was%20given%20a%20forehead%20tilak%20of%20blood%20in%20Ujjain%20by%20militants%20of%20VHP.%20Songs%2C%20slogans%20and%20speeches%20exhorted%20communal%20sentiments%20and%20demonised%20Muslims%2C%20inciting%20communal%20conflict%20throughout%20the%20itinerary.%20They%20were%20clearly%20designed%20to%20create%20Hindu%20militancy%20and%20raise%20the%20religious%20consciousness%20of%20Hindus%20on%20communal%20lines.%20The%20outcome%20was%20predictable.%20Town%20after%20town%20succumbed%20to%20riots%2C%20arson%2C%20killings%2C%20and%20curfew.%20The%20Yatra%20resulted%20in%20communal%20riots%20in%20most%20of%20the%20cities%2C%20spreading%20anti-muslim%20evocation%20of%20violent%20politics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBacked%20by%20planned%20rumours%20and%20incendiary%20propaganda%2C%20the%20Yatra%20succeeded%20in%20creating%20a%20geography%20of%20violence%20and%20aggrandised%20communal%20polarisation.%20The%20riots%20shaped%20the%20social%20psyche%20of%20the%20Hindus%20to%20embrace%20the%20religious%20identity%20and%20rally%20behind%20the%20cause%20of%20Ram%20Mandir.%20The%20cynical%20exploitation%20of%20religious%20imagery%20for%20political%20ends%20made%20the%20BJP%20the%20natural%20party%20of%20Hindus.%20This%20yatra%2C%20engineered%20by%20Advani%2C%20brought%20fortunes%20to%20the%20BJP%20which%20witnessed%20an%20astounding%20political%20success%20in%20subsequent%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20principles%20of%20law%20and%20Rath%20Yatra%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20yatra%2C%20Advani%20showed%20an%20open%20disregard%20for%20the%20land%20of%20law%2C%20constitutional%20principles%20of%20secularism%20and%20adjudicatory%20powers%20of%20the%20Indian%20judiciary.%20He%20found%20the%20temple%20movement%20to%20be%20a%20matter%20of%20popular%20Hindu%20faith%20that%20could%20not%20be%20decided%20by%20science%2C%20history%2C%20or%20law.%20He%20questioned%20the%20secular%20principles%20of%20the%20constitution%20and%20demanded%20that%20the%20Hindu%20sovereignty%20over%20the%20sacred%20space%20be%20granted%20and%20that%20the%20judiciary%20should%20not%20adjudicate%20matters%20of%20faith.%20Time%20flattened%20these%20appeals%20of%20Advani%20as%20Ram%20Temple%20stands%20on%20the%20ruins%20of%20the%20Mosque%2C%20as%20decided%20by%20the%20judiciary%20and%20inaugurated%20by%20the%20Indian%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20anything%2C%20Advani%20curated%20the%20current%20brand%20of%20Hindutva%20politics.%20The%20culture%20of%20mob%20violence%20and%20Hindu%20majoritarian%20politics%20have%20trumped%20electoral%20politics.%20Hindutva%20has%20become%20the%20hegemonic%20political%20discourse%20and%20minorities%20are%20being%20relegated%20to%20a%20substandard%20location.%20Secular%20credentials%20of%20the%20constitutions%20are%20subverted%20by%20the%20Indian%20state.%20From%20dormant%20to%20a%20hegemonic%20political%20mainstream%2C%20the%20Hindutva%20politics%20of%20BJP%20grew%20in%20the%20shadow%20of%2