ps%20extends%20to%20individuals%20who%20%26quot%3Bany%20resident%20of%20Uttarakhand...%20in%20a%20live-in%20relationship%20outside%20the%20State%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Flive-in-relationships%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELive-in%20relationships%3C%2Fa%3E%20will%20not%20be%20registered%20in%20cases%20that%20are%20%26quot%3Bagainst%20public%20policy%20and%20morality%26quot%3B%2C%20if%20one%20partner%20is%20married%20or%20in%20another%20relationship%2C%20if%20one%20partner%20is%20a%20minor%2C%20and%20if%20consent%20of%20one%20partner%20was%20obtained%20by%20%26quot%3Bcoercion%2C%20fraud%2C%20or%20misrepresentation%20(with%20regard%20to%20identity)%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20senior%20official%20told%20NDTV%20a%20website%20is%20being%20prepped%20to%20accept%20details%20of%20live-in%20relationship%2C%20which%20will%20be%20verified%20with%20the%20District%20Registrar%2C%20who%20will%20conduct%20a%20%26quot%3Bsummary%20inquiry%26quot%3B%20to%20establish%20the%20validity%20of%20the%20relationship.%20To%20do%20so%2C%20he%20may%20summon%20either%20or%20both%20partners%2C%20or%20anybody%20else.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShould%20registration%20be%20refused%2C%20the%20Registrar%20must%20inform%20in%20writing%20his%2Fher%20reasons.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%26quot%3Btermination%26quot%3B%20of%20registered%20live-in%20relationships%20requires%20a%20written%20statement%2C%20in%20a%20%26quot%3Bprescribed%20format%26quot%3B%20that%20can%20invite%20police%20investigation%20if%20the%20Registrar%20feels%20reasons%20for%20the%20relationship%20ending%20are%20%26quot%3Bincorrect%26quot%3B%20or%20%26quot%3Bsuspicious%26quot%3B.%20Parents%20or%20guardians%20of%20those%20under%2021%20will%20also%20be%20informed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFailure%20to%20submit%20live-in%20relationship%20declarations%2C%20or%20providing%20false%20information%2C%20could%20land%20one%20in%20jail%20for%20three%20months%2C%20a%20fine%20of%20Rs%2025