gh%20it%20does%20not%20specify%20what%20constitutes%20%26quot%3Bdesertion%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EUttarakhand's%20Uniform%20Civil%20Code%3A%20Explained%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20Uniform%20Civil%20Code%2C%20or%20UCC%20refers%20to%20a%20set%20of%20laws%20applicable%20to%20all%20citizens%2C%20and%20is%20not%20based%20on%20religion%20when%20dealing%20with%20marriage%2C%20divorce%2C%20inheritance%2C%20and%20adoption%2C%20among%20other%20personal%20matters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20common%20civil%20code%20for%20Uttarakhand%20was%20one%20of%20the%20major%20poll%20promises%20made%20by%20the%20BJP%20in%20the%20run-up%20to%20last%20year's%20assembly%20election%2C%20which%20the%20party%20won.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20State-appointed%20panel%2C%20led%20by%20a%20retired%20Supreme%20Court%20judge%2C%20has%20drafted%20a%20749-page%20document%20based%20on%20a%20reported%202.33%20lakh%20pieces%20of%20written%20feedback%20and%20engagement%20with%2060%2C000%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20of%20the%20proposals%20include%20a%20complete%20ban%20on%20polygamy%20and%20child%20marriage%2C%20a%20standardised%20marriageable%20age%20for%20girls%20across%20all%20faiths%2C%20and%20a%20uniform%20process%20for%20divorce.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUttarakhand's%20UCC%20also%20seeks%20to%20ban%20practices%20like%20'%3Cem%3Ehalala%3C%2Fem%3E'%20and%20'%3Cem%3Eiddat%3C%2Fem%3E'%2C%20which%20are%20the%20Islamic%20practices%20a%20woman%20must%20go%20through%20after%20a%20divorce%20or%20the%20death%20of%20the%20husband.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fassam-to-implement-uniform-civil-code-in-2024-tribals-to-be-exempted-chief-minister-himanta-biswa-sarma-4842909%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAssam%20To%20Implement%20Uniform%20Civil%20Code%20In%202024%2C%20Tribals%20Exempt%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUttarakhand%20isn't%20the%20only%20state%20to%20be%20pushing%20a%20uniform%