er%20digital%20payments%20platform.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIPO%20Backlash%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPaytm's%202021%20IPO%20valuation%20faced%20a%20backlash%20from%20investors%20and%20analysts%20when%20the%20stock%20plummeted%20on%20its%20debut.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20company's%20IPO%20opened%20on%20November%208%2C%202021%2C%20in%20the%20price%20band%20of%20Rs%202%2C080-2%2C150%20per%20share.%20The%20Paytm%20IPO%20made%20history%20with%20over%20Rs%2018%2C300%20crore%20share%20sale%20making%20it%20the%20largest%20public%20issue%20in%20India's%20corporate%20history.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20company's%20stock%20made%20a%20weak%20debut%20in%20the%20market%20on%20November%2018%20and%20hit%20a%20lower%20circuit%20after%20recording%20about%2020%20per%20cent%20decline%20during%20trading%20hours.%20It%20finally%20closed%20at%20Rs%201%2C560%2C%20down%20by%20about%2027%20per%20cent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20firm's%20big%20backer%20SoftBank%20recently%20pared%20its%20stake%2C%20while%20other%20key%20investors%20Alibaba%20and%20Buffett's%20Berkshire%20Hathway%20sold%20their%20holdings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERevenue%20Sources%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPaytm%20has%20two%20major%20sources%20of%20revenue%20-%20its%20merchant%20payment%20business%20and%20loan%20business.%20Merchant%20payments%20constitutes%20roughly%2060%25%20of%20total%20income%20and%20loans%20account%20for%20about%2020%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20fintech%20company%20charges%20merchants%20a%20platform%20fee%20to%20use%20Paytm's%20payment%20gateway%2C%20among%20other%20subscription-based%20services%20and%20products%20such%20as%20a%20soundbox%20and%20card%20swipe%20machine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20provides%20loans%20under%20partnerships%20with%20some%20banks%20and%20non-bank%20financial%20companies%2C%20taking%20a%20cut%20of%20the%20interest.%20Paytm%20Payments%20Bank%20was%20one%20of%20these%20entities%20through%20which%20it%20provided%20loans.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERBI%20Crackdown%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20RBI%20last%20week%20ordered%20Paytm%20Payments%20Bank%20to%20wind%20down%20most%20of%20its%20businesses%2C%20including%20deposits%2C%20credit%20products%20and%20its%20popular%20wallet%20by%20February%2029%20for%20%26quot%3Bpersistent%20non-compliances%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bsupervisory%20concerns%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHundreds%20of%20accounts%20created%20on%20Paytm%20Payments%20Bank%20without%20proper%20identification%20were%20one%20of%20the%20major%20reasons%20behind%20the%20RBI%20imposing%20stringent%20curbs%20on%20the%20company%2C%20reports%20quoted%20sources%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20RBI%20is%20concerned%20that%20some%20of%20the%20accounts%20could%20have%20been%20used%20for%20money%20laundering%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20post%20assuring%20users%2C%20Vijay%20Shekhar%20Sharma%20has%20described%20the%20RBI's%20action%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bspeed%20bump%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707204000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2021-11%2Fcac3fqc8_vijay-shekhar-sharma-paytm-reuters-650_625x300_18_November_21.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpaytm-vijay-shekhar-sharma-rbi-paytm-wallet-paytms-vijay-shekhar-sharma-a-rags-to-riches-star-of-start-up-ecosystem-5003661%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Vijay%20Shekhar%20Sharma%2C%20one%20of%20the%20most%20recognised%20faces%20of%20India's%20fintech%20industry%2C%20is%20facing%20a%20big%20crisis%20in%20a%20race%20to%20save%20his%20revolutionary%20digital%20payments%20firm%20-%20Paytm.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpaytm-vijay-shekhar-sharma-rbi-paytm-wallet-paytms-vijay-shekhar-sharma-a-rags-to-riches-star-of-start-up-ecosystem-5003661%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpaytm-vijay-shekhar-sharma-rbi-paytm-wallet-paytms-vijay-shekhar-sharma-a-rags-to-riches-star-of-start-up-ecosystem-5003661%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpaytm-vijay-shekhar-sharma-rbi-paytm-wallet-paytms-vijay-shekhar-sharma-a-rags-to-riches-star-of-start-up-ecosystem-5003661%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Hyundai%20Said%20To%20Be%20Considering%20One%20Of%20India's%20Biggest%20Ever%20IPOs%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EHyundai%20Motor%20Co.%20is%20considering%20an%20initial%20public%20offering%20for%20its%20India%20unit%20that%20may%20raise%20about%20%242.5%20billion%2C%20according%20to%20people%20familiar%20with%20the%20matter%2C%20potentially%20making%20it%20one%20of%20the%20biggest%20listings%20ever%20in%20the%20South%20Asian%20country.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHyundai%20has%20held%20talks%20with%20international%20banks%20about%20the%20possible%20IPO%2C%20the%20people%20said%2C%20asking%20not%20to%20be%20identified%20discussing%20confidential%20information.%20The%20company%20may%20reach%20out%20to%20domestic%20advisers%20for%20pitches%20soon%2C%20one%20of%20the%20people%20said.%20A%20listing%20may%20value%20the%20Indian%20unit%20at%20%2425%20billion%2C%20the%20people%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConsiderations%20are%20at%20a%20very%20early%20stage%20and%20a%20share%20sale%20may%20not%20go%20ahead%2C%20the%20people%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20representative%20for%20Hyundai%20Motor%20India%20Ltd.%20declined%20to%20comment%20and%20the%20parent%20company%20didn't%20immediately%20respond%20to%20requests%20for%20comment.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20an%20IPO%20does%20proceed%2C%20Hyundai%20will%20use%20the%20cash%20raised%20to%20expand%20operations%2C%20one%20of%20the%20people%20said.%20India%20is%20a%20key%20market%20that%20accounted%20for%2013%25%20of%20Hyundai's%20global%20sales%20last%20year%20and%20the%20South%20Korean%20firm%20is%20the%20country's%20second-biggest%20carmaker.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShares%20of%20Hyundai's%20comp