20three%20to%20four%20years.%20The%20initiative%20works%20on%20dual%20fronts%20%E2%80%94%20providing%20training%20to%20teachers%20in%20STEM%20education%20and%20building%20physical%20infrastructure%20in%20schools%2C%20including%20STEM%20labs%20or%20digital%20classrooms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20process%20begins%20with%20L%26amp%3BT%20selecting%20a%20school%2C%20and%20conducting%20an%20orientation%20and%20a%20needs%20assessment.%20A%20key%20criterion%20is%20the%20presence%20of%20a%20science%20teacher%2C%20and%20the%20initiative%20is%20tailored%20for%20students%20in%20Classes%206%20to%209.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWorking%20through%20NGO%20partners%2C%20L%26amp%3BT%20delivers%20training%20to%20the%20district%20education%20officer%2C%20school%20principal%2C%20and%20teachers.%20Quarterly%20training%20sessions%20are%20conducted%20for%20teachers%2C%20with%20an%20observer%20present%20in%20the%20classroom%20to%20evaluate%20the%20effectiveness%20of%20teaching%20and%20provide%20guidance%20on%20improvement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20hands-on%20approach%20not%20only%20equips%20teachers%20to%20impart%20knowledge%20effectively%20but%20also%20strives%20to%20establish%20a%20sustainable%20model.%20The%20goal%20is%20to%20empower%20teachers%20to%20continue%20delivering%20quality%20education%20independently%2C%20even%20without%20ongoing%20assistance%20from%20the%20NGO.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20idea%20is%20to%20improve%20children%E2%80%99s%20conceptual%20understanding%20of%20science.%20Based%20on%20our%20observation%2C%20many%20students%20lose%20interest%20in%20science%20in%20Classes%206%20to%209.%20Girl%20students%20too%20face%20several%20biases%20and%20challenges%20as%20STEM%20courses%20are%20not%20traditionally%20considered%20a%20woman%E2%80%99s%20domain.%20If%20they%20get%20a%20better%20understanding%20of%20scientific%20concepts%20through%20innovative%20methods%2C%20there%20is%20a%20possibility%20of%20them%20choosing%20a%20career%20in%20science%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Mabel.%3C%2