5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20mentions%20that%20they%20also%20employed%20blind%20tasting%20to%20assess%20their%20products%20with%20consumers.%20According%20to%20Ahana%2C%20their%20Unique%20Selling%20Proposition%20(USP)%20lies%20in%20the%20fact%20that%20their%20product%20replicates%20the%20taste%20of%20junk%20food%2C%20fulfilling%20people%E2%80%99s%20cravings%20healthily.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20they%20slowly%20started%20building%20their%20presence%2C%20they%20faced%20their%20first%20roadblock%20two%20months%20later%20as%20COVID-19%20hit%20India.%20Not%20one%20to%20bow%20down%20during%20a%20crisis%2C%20Ahana%20worked%20on%20converting%20it%20into%20an%20opportunity.%20They%20focused%20on%20online%20channels%20and%20were%20able%20to%20operate%20during%20the%20lockdown%20as%20they%20fell%20under%20the%20essential%20categories%20list.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20hustled%20through%20COVID-19.%20Once%2C%20the%20cooling%20refrigeration%20system%20at%20the%20factory%20stopped%20working%20during%20the%20lockdown.%20We%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20get%20any%20technician%20but%20needed%20a%20refrigerator%20to%20store%20our%20chocolates%20and%20products.%20I%20brought%20my%20refrigerator%20from%20home%20and%20that%E2%80%99s%20how%20we%20averted%20a%20major%20crisis%2C%E2%80%9D%20laughs%20Ahana.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20make%20themselves%20visible%20online%2C%20they%20used%20banners%20and%20discounts%2C%20and%20placed%20their%20products%20across%20online%20channels.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20founder%20states%20that%20they%20grew%20multi-fold%20amid%20the%20pandemic%20and%20sold%20over%2010%20lakh%20cookies.%20Since%20then%2C%20there%20has%20been%20no%20looking%20back.%20Open%20Secret%20sells%20over%2030%20products%2C%20including%20cookies%2C%20biscuits%2C%20chips%2C%20dry%20fruits%2C%20snacks%2C%20chocolates%2C%20brownies%2C%20cereals%20and%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20are%20present%20across%20online%20channels%20including%20Amazon%2C%20Flipkart%2C%20their%20own%20website%2C%20and%20quick%20commerce%20chains%20like%20Zepto%2C%20Blinkit%2C%20Big%20Basket%20and%20more.%20They%20also%20sell%20through%20supermarkets%20offline.%20Through%20their%20platform%2C%20they%20also%20partner%20with%20and%20sell%20products%20from%20over%20100%20healthy%20brands.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAhana%20states%20that%20they%20will%20achieve%20gross%20sales%20of%20Rs%20100%20crore%20this%20year%20and%20wants%20to%20become%20a%20Rs%2010%2C000%20crore%20company%20in%20the%20coming%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98An%20ode%20to%20my%20mother%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201083px)%20100vw%2C%201083px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FOpen7-1706874286.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221083%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ahana%20studied%20at%20Harvard%20Business%20School%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FOpen7-1706874286.jpeg%201083w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FOpen7-1706874286-227x300.jpeg%20227w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FOpen7-1706874286-500x660.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FOpen7-1706874286-768x1014.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FOpen7-1706874286-150x198.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-340618%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221430%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EAhana%20studied%20at%20Harvard%20Business%20School.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOpen%20Secret%E2%80%99s%20USP%2C%20besides%20its%20snacks%2C%20is%20its%20women%2C%20says%20Ahana.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%20factories%20are%20run%20by%20200%20women%20and%20over%2050%20percent%20of%20its%20employees%20are%20women.%20Why%3F%20Ahana%20believes%20tha