hese%20innovators%20is%20Suresh%20S%20R%2C%20a%2050-year-old%20areca%20palm%20grower%20from%20Shivamogga%2C%20who%20has%20developed%20a%20100%20percent%20natural%2C%20chemical-free%20vegan%20leather%20made%20out%20of%20areca%20leaves%20and%20husk.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20wanted%20to%20do%20something%20innovative%20and%20good%20for%20the%20environment%20because%20we%20take%20a%20lot%20from%20nature%20and%20give%20back%20nothing.%20So%20I%20thought%20of%20working%20towards%20reducing%20the%20massive%20amount%20of%20carbon%20emission%20caused%20by%20the%20leather%20industry%2C%E2%80%9D%20Suresh%2C%20who%20is%20the%20co-founder%20of%20Bhoomi%20Agri%20Ventures%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Growing%20up%20in%20nature%20motivated%20me%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuresh%20was%20born%20in%20a%20small%20town%20in%20Karnataka%20called%20Sringeri.%20%E2%80%9CComing%20from%20an%20agricultural%20family%2C%20growing%20up%2C%20all%20I%20saw%20around%20me%20was%20nature.%20I%20remember%20running%20around%20in%20the%20farms%20and%20feeling%20blissful%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says%2C%20adding%20that%20areca%20palm%20trees%20were%20abundant%20in%20his%20town.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAreca%20plant%20is%20a%20primary%20commercial%20crop%20in%20the%20southern%20districts%20of%20Karnataka%2C%20covering%20more%20than%20one%20lakh%20hectares%20of%20land.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20so%20common%20for%20us%20to%20spot%20them%20growing%20around%20the%20house%20and%20in%20the%20neighbourhood.%20I%20would%20tear%20its%20leaves%20and%20play%20with%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fleather-1-1706853691.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Footwear%20made%20out%20of%20areca%